high_descs: Turn left to reach the bedroom and walk to the sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the nightstand.
Turn right to head to the sink on the left.
Cut the lettuce in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up the lettuce slice from the sink.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to exit the bedroom and reach the fridge on the left.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around and head to the room on the right and reach the sidetable.
Put the slice of lettuce on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled lettuce slice on the SideTable.

high_descs: Go straight and take the door on the left into the bedroom, approaching the sidetable near to the door to the right of that room.
Pick up the knife from the bedstand.
Go through the doorway on the right, then turn left to the bathroom.
Slice the lettuce inside the bathroom sink.
Place the knife down on the sink.
Pick up some lettuce.
Exit the bathroom, the small room, and the bedroom the way you came in, then go straight ahead and slightly to the left to the kitchen area, turning left to the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, let it cool, then retrieve it.
Return to the sidetable you got the knife from.
Place the lettuce down on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Slice some lettuce, cool some of it in a fridge and place it on a SideTable.

high_descs: Keep going. Turn left. Go inside and turn right, when you get to the door, move a little and then turn left when you get to the sidetable.
Grab the knife.
Turn around, move a little and turn left. Enter the room and then turn left.
Open the lettuce.
Cut a piece of lettuce. Place the knife in the sink.
Grab the lettuce.
Turn around. Exit the room. When you get near the bed, turn left. Go straight to the furniture. Turn left and after the cabinet, turn right. Go inside and turn left in front of the fridge.
Open the top doors of the shelf. Place the piece of lettuce on the left side. Close the doors. Wait 6 seconds. Open the doors. Take out the piece of lettuce. Close the doors.
